Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:08.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}终于找到了  全新的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:12.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}日月却来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:17.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}我前往的地方  不是“未来”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:21.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仅仅不停地追赶着“过去”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}不停地鸣响着 那过去的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:32.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}仿佛无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:37.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}差不多了吧  那厌倦搜索的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:42.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}丢掉心里的纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:47.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  总有会停的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:53.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这么漫长  却如此冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:58.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  为什么会选择我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}笼罩着我  真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:07.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雨  已经忘了停
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.87,0:01:13.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}今天依然持续下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:18.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在默默撑开的雨伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:29.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}接近那温暖的怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:32.49,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}从那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:36.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}就决定不再哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:42.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur2}即使承担再多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:47.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仍有无法原谅的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:50.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经无法回到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:53.35,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:58.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还没有做成任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:03.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的记忆之碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:09.57,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}又有一块  消逝而去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回望今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:20.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}期望这个声音总有一天可以传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.84,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:25.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在风停止的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.26,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}仰望天空追寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:37.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}在黎明前散发的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:43.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}将会变成彩虹

Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}不死的军团
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说多数个体的实验还没进行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是实验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵从我们命令战斗的最强士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不死的军团诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你们的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意 好好听我接下来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下有多个叛乱分子想进攻这个司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的气氛让我感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和阿尔说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,66号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开膛手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是切片手的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.22,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么打开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让正与布里克斯兵以及马斯坦古战斗的中央兵撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要开枪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你没好好教育部下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点让他们撤退的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里克斯兵会毫不客气地继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让你的士兵一个都不剩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把中央司令部东西南北所有的门都关上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许布里克斯兵和马斯坦古一伙进入这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然腐败 但倒也不是没有骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太得意了 娘们儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们布里克斯的山猴子轻松就能碾碎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到命令 打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的位子又空了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让我阿姆斯壮家代代相传的名刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用染上那肮脏的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把灵魂装到人偶里了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 不断涌出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些东西是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 如果把这些家伙放出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是马斯坦古大佐发起政变了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 他们要到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 把出口封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不干 我也会把出口打坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也能下定决心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就是我们大显身手的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然造出这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不突破这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法打飞胡子大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点艰难 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古坐上冰淇淋店的卡车逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封锁主要道路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然装成民用车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡车里装着武器和弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊 熊？剃了莫西干头的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,断了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剃了莫西干头的熊到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北方军的帕卡尼亚大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐 要进入市内看来很难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰淇淋店的卡车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们进行得顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 不能成为战力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是让人牙痒痒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到只是等待会这么闷得慌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音从昨天开始就一直持续着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯 这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰利姆在用我的头玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然里面是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但终究是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止他 阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这声音停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫尔斯电码 是军用的通信符号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在传达这里的位置…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 谢谢你来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 别给我增加多余的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就原谅我吧 不会再大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我 恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没骗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面有长生不老…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛 痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这婊子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么军人会来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是来强拆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可难办了 没有其他可去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是发现了我们躲藏的地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你的身份暴露了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能就这么见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你成了人质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而会拖阿尔冯斯的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能随便乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.44,0:14:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就乖乖待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说库拉多尼也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把同伴吃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是同伴 是共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是同一个父亲生出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过又回归一体了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨克尔先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是合成兽 生命力真强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨克尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无谓的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不起作用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 阿姆斯壮少将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面以反叛罪的名义 下达了射杀你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要在这种情况下把兵放在一处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微受点伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次没弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉女将军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为在和谁说话 亚力士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹对他完全无效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大炮等级才起点作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我擅长的领域吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你弟弟亚力士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么下去会一起完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢下我的话 说不定你还能逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只考虑活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是金普利和普莱德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点动 这条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们绝不能输在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亨克尔先生 抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们兄弟真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么自己也伤痕累累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想救别人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哥哥一起发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不再让任何人死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 活下来的就是胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金普利那家伙也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来拿着个好东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么亨克尔先生会拿着这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在北方的废矿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被金普利抛弃的时候捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤者之石…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这个的话可能会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用人的生命制造出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也从你哥哥那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不想用这个来恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样 那就不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护世界而使用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经成为这样的石头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还承认这是人的生命 所以才拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都想为了守护自己最宝贵的东西而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也让他们参加战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去揍他们一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起战斗吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人的土尘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用暴风吹散它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 两个人还在灰尘里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就凭那双脚是没法逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是…别说逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔冯斯·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是人与人的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.09,0:24:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沿着自己的信念前进
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕全身是泥而犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是愚蠢的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第52话 大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷茫的时刻 已经过去了
